{"tid":1620074,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"覺得長時間帶口罩好辛苦既入黎","createTime":"2019-10-04T09:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T12:40:37.000Z","uid":254898,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"22e9358c81d6b4cf5809409e8da6df1513bb64d5","tid":1620074,"uid":254898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:22:53.000Z","msg":"今日係全民口罩日呀<br />\n我地最基本要帶口罩表達反對禁蒙面法呀<br />\n拎左口罩既唔該時刻帶翻上個口到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你唔係凈係帶比自己睇架<br />\n所以唔好凈係係自己個自閉班房或者公司個自閉位度帶<br />\n最重要係出到街搭緊車要帶著呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以除左食飯飲水，只要係屋企外就要帶著呀<br />\n你真係病左或者預防傳染病都唔會特登係多人既地方除咁諷刺啦<br />\n記住帶口罩係想表態呀<br />\n香港病左呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n帶口罩係保護自己，保護他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要帶到比身邊既同事/同學/行人/街坊/甚至樓下個保安都見到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9FkwE3y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9FkwE3y.jpg&h=1fbf7464&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"434c44973fcc6906acc9ef7b3ab50bacc5499de0","tid":1620074,"uid":254898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:24:23.000Z","msg":"唔該放工放學一定帶翻上個口度呀！！"},{"pid":"d158d1921f46fffdca5bca2325b93cf3d6801b16","tid":1620074,"uid":254898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:25:26.000Z","msg":"唔好怕尷尬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ddd7a4766520ef59f4ebc29fc2d0419613e40d","tid":1620074,"uid":49753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:26:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命<br />\n全民起義 還政於民<br />\n驅逐共黨 香港獨立<br />\n</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"32aea4f45400196e80ccf47de3ec49ea2bb0fbd8","tid":1620074,"uid":254898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:26:27.000Z","msg":"最基本既表態<br />\n一定要做到呀"},{"pid":"2021d0734d332d68e6aac1e29109046854185d91","tid":1620074,"uid":254898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21ddd7a4766520ef59f4ebc29fc2d0419613e40d","tid":1620074,"uid":49753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:26:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命<br />\n全民起義 還政於民<br />\n驅逐共黨 香港獨立<br />\n</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:27:18.000Z","msg":"還政於民 勢在必行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"074f97cf8a407069ab7f7825485d50631097ce26","tid":1620074,"uid":254898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:28:35.000Z","msg":"今日怕辛苦唔帶，聽日比人拉冇得帶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e46f7e686e9d9ca4ec2a42945f21b9fbe998010c","tid":1620074,"uid":259329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:28:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"030a77b3995c29bb0611ec54cb376636696cd434","tid":1620074,"uid":254898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e46f7e686e9d9ca4ec2a42945f21b9fbe998010c","tid":1620074,"uid":259329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:28:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:29:26.000Z","msg":"部機自焚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"264b9c09158644b6fa10f493074a0d3a53cb49