 />\n而家香港人都得！！！！"},{"pid":"895b4fa92e1994e4578ea8d7d0d17f2a9bdd1034","tid":1620074,"uid":254898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ba5671fdf7de35b0073e0007b041a8393d02557","tid":1620074,"uid":10064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:48:07.000Z","msg":"只要當係當年sars 咁就得<br />\nsars 都頂到<br />\n而家香港人都得！！！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:49:41.000Z","msg":"香港病左，保護自己，保護他人，以防墮落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a72d7f931829e0251b06e5ddccee2de526b12e5","tid":1620074,"uid":271173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:52:30.000Z","msg":"我咁岩都係買呢款黑口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過一直都有一個麻煩，<br />\n戴耐左耳仔會痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過都阻止唔到我戴足全日架！"},{"pid":"24e43043475f08e9842d3f3a78cb9a44c02c1cd5","tid":1620074,"uid":254898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a72d7f931829e0251b06e5ddccee2de526b12e5","tid":1620074,"uid":271173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:52:30.000Z","msg":"我咁岩都係買呢款黑口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過一直都有一個麻煩，<br />\n戴耐左耳仔會痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過都阻止唔到我戴足全日架！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:55:36.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27fb753a73e19b4055011843259bb5faaf4768e4","tid":1620074,"uid":218193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:02:25.000Z","msg":"最近轉季，唔好比人傳染流感"}]}